com.vmware.appliance

Interface SupportBundle

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Service, SupportBundleTypes
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SupportBundleStub

    public interface SupportBundle
extends Service, SupportBundleTypes
    The SupportBundle interface provides methods to create support bundle task, cancel, list and list components. This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.1.0.
